description: This file is a C header file (.h) that declares interfaces and function prototypes for the HTTP Simple Proxy Object within an HTTP implementation. It includes licensing information, macro guards, and declarations of creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions related to the proxy object.

methods.name: HttpCreateSimpleProxy
methods.description: Creates an instance of the HTTP Simple Proxy object, taking container context, owner context, and reserved handle as parameters.

methods.name: HttpSpoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the HTTP Proxy object with given contexts.

methods.name: HttpSpoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified proxy object instance.

methods.name: HttpSpoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls or registers necessary objects within the proxy object.
